1.0.0.name: wordpress/google-plus-google
1.0.0.description:
Google Plus Plugin for WordPress allows you to Add Google Plus Widgets, Google Api Console required. Simple and fast, just paste your google plus profile ID under "GP Dashboard" Option Page after installed.

Google Plus Plugin Features
  1. Google Plus Stream
  2. Google Plus Profile
  3. Google Plus One
